What our guests are saying
“ Last weekend I got married in Key West which was all around an awesome time. But the icing on the cake was the after party at the Irish Kevin’s loft. Daylin was my point of contact in arranging the event and she was hands down the most accommodating and friendliest person I’ve met in Key West, no exaggeration. From start (planning) to finish (last call) she treated us like family! ”

“ We had a pre-wedding party of about 20 people in KW last weekend. I contacted IK’s about their private party and the upstairs. Daylin at IK’s contacted me very soon and, despite my short notice, was able to take care our group in every way. We had a private bartender, security and restrooms. Daylin also personally took care our food arrangements. It was a huge hit and we can’t wait to have another party there. The entertainment is always great but anyone with a larger group needs to consider the upstairs. It makes a great experience even better. Thanks again to the staff at IK’s!! ”

“ Irish Kevin’s was the fourth stop on my husband and my’s wedding bar crawl in January. Daylin and Irish Kevin’s did a wonderful job hosting 70 plus people on the balcony. We cut the cake here and Daylin set up a beautiful table and took delivery of the cake from our baker so we had nothing to worry about. The band brought us newlyweds on stage for a rousing number and the entire experience was perfect. Thank you Irish Kevin’s for hosting us – see you next year!! ”
